name: AT-AT Deployment Platform
LocationDStext: May deploy Biker Scout Gear here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle, and while here, once per turn, may deploy one card (without ability) in its game text from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
LocationLStext: Your characters may enter/exit here for 2 Force each.  Unless you occupy, AT-AT's immunity to attrition is +1 (or immune to attrition if non-unique).
